### **4. 24_RealtimePlotDock**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes incoming numeric values in a live-updating line chart for dashboards and monitors.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealtimePlotDock - Live Stream Chart Renderer

RealtimePlotDock creates a clean, interactive chart from real-time data sources for monitoring pipelines or sensor input.

## Features
- Live scrolling chart  
- Matplotlib powered  
- Easy-to-configure stream input  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_RealtimePlotDock.git
cd 24_RealtimePlotDock
python visualize.py
